Subject: [PATCH 001/117] feat(session): add agent_session_id field and helper
 functions

- Add agent_session_id field to Instance struct with serde support
- Add generate_claude_session_id() for UUID generation
- Add capture_opencode_session_id() for CLI query
- Add capture_codex_session_id() for filesystem scan
- Add build_resume_flags() for tool-specific flag construction
- Add comprehensive tests for serde behavior and flag construction

