Subject: [PATCH 003/117] test(session): add comprehensive unit tests for
 session ID persistence

Add edge case tests:
- Agent switch clears session ID
- Empty string session ID handling
- Capture failure graceful degradation
- Resume with invalid session ID
- Backwards compatibility with old JSON

Part of #343
---
