- OpenCode: add directory matching and retry logic (3 attempts, 2s delay)
- Codex: support date-partitioned dirs, sort by mtime, respect CODEX_HOME
- Sandbox: route opencode/codex capture through docker exec with host fallback
- Claude: use --resume flag instead of --session-id (idiomatic CLI usage)
- CLI: add 'aoe session set-session-id <identifier> <session-id>' command
