Encode each agent's session-resume mechanism (flag, flag-pair, subcommand, or none) as a typed enum on AgentDef, replacing ad-hoc string matching in the resume-flags builder.

Ultraworked with [Sisyphus](https://github.com/code-yeongyu/oh-my-opencode)

