Subject: [PATCH 031/117] refactor(session): improve robustness, reduce
 duplication, and harden implementation

- Extract apply_session_flags() to deduplicate 3 acquire+append call sites
- Extract persist_session_to_storage() free function for shared persist logic
- Pass SessionConfig into poll/capture functions (avoid per-tick config reload)
- Unify filter logic in capture_from_container via filter_opencode_sessions()
- SessionPoller::start() returns bool for spawn success feedback
- Store and join deferred capture thread handle on kill/restart
- Use pid_t type alias for platform-correct process ID cast
- Upgrade persist failure log levels from debug to warn
- Document cmd.find(' ') unquoted-path assumption
