 guard, validation helpers, and filesystem resilience

Audit all session management code and fix 8 findings:
- Replace load-check-increment poller counter with CAS-loop RAII PollerCountGuard
- Remove cross-project session fallbacks (codex, gemini, vibe)
- Return None for non-UUID codex filenames instead of garbage strings
- Add session ID validation at all capture boundaries via validated_session_id helper
- Add debug_assert to prevent persist_session_to_storage from background threads
- Extract resilient_read_dir helper to gracefully skip unreadable dir entries
- Add #[serial] to tmux env cache tests sharing global RwLock
- Fix clippy warnings (len_zero, needless_bool_assign)
