- Extract apply_yolo_mode() helper to deduplicate 3 identical yolo blocks
- Extract extract_cwd_from_json() helper for Gemini/Vibe CWD extraction
- Make publish_session_to_tmux_env() return Result with proper error handling
- Add error logging to silent JSON parse failures in hook install/uninstall
- Use symlink_metadata() instead of metadata() in status_file.rs
- Add diagnostic logging to tmux env batch fallback path
