From: =?UTF-8?q?J=C3=A9r=C3=B4me=20Benoit?= <jerome.benoit@sap.com>
Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 17:57:38 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 116/117] fix(session): eliminate race on AOE_INSTANCE_ID and
 validate poller session IDs

- Set AOE_INSTANCE_ID synchronously in finalize_launch before starting
  the poller, preventing build_exclusion_set from self-excluding on the
  first poll tick
- Add validated_session_id gate to all 5 poll closures and the TUI
  receiver, matching the defense-in-depth pattern from try_retroactive_capture
- Wrap finalize-tmux background thread in catch_unwind to surface panics
- Batch build_exclusion_set tmux env reads via get_hidden_env_batch
- Update hooks install dialog text to match current hook format
